-- Death Toll From China Storms, Flooding Has Risen to 88, Government Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-19T05:08:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-19/death-toll-from-china-storms-flooding-has-risen-to-88-government-says.html

          
          
             The death toll from the storms and
flooding in eight provinces across China rose to 88 as of 10
a.m. today, the Ministry of Civil Affairs said on its website.
The bad weather has caused direct economic losses estimated at
11 billion yuan, the ministry said.  
